        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_earthshaker_enchant_totem_Description": "Verstärkt Earthshakers Totem, sodass es beim nächsten Schlag zusätzlichen Schaden verursacht.",
        "[english]DOTA_Tooltip_ability_earthshaker_enchant_totem_Description": "Empowers Earthshaker's totem, causing it to deal extra damage on the next attack.",
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_earthshaker_enchant_totem_Lore": "Raigors Gorilla-Stärke kann Berge zerstören.",
        "[english]DOTA_Tooltip_ability_earthshaker_enchant_totem_Lore": "Raigor's gorilla strength can destroy mountains.",
