        "[english]DOTA_Tooltip_ability_riki_backstab_Description": "If Riki attacks from behind, bonus damage is applied based on his current agility.",
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_riki_backstab_Lore": "Der Stealth Assassin ist sich nicht zu schade, schmutzig zu kämpfen, und greift seine Gegner gerne hinterrücks an.",
        "[english]DOTA_Tooltip_ability_riki_backstab_Lore": "The Stealth Assassin is not afraid to fight dirty, and specializes in attacking his opponents from behind.",
