        "[english]DOTA_Tooltip_ability_beastmaster_primal_roar_Description": "A deafening roar that deals damage and stuns the target enemy unit, while opening a path between Beastmaster and his prey. Nearby enemies also take damage and have their movement speed and attack rate reduced.\n\nUpgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.",
