        "[english]DOTA_Tooltip_ability_venomancer_poison_nova_Description": "A spreading ring of poison that does damage over time to enemy units around Venomancer.  Poison Nova's effect cannot bring units below 1 HP.\n\nUpgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.",
