        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_luna_eclipse_Description": "Beschwört mehrere Lucent Beams, um Gegner in der Umgebung zu schädigen.",
        "[english]DOTA_Tooltip_ability_luna_eclipse_Description": "Calls an eclipse that follows Luna, striking units with her current level of Lucent Beam.  A single target can only be hit a maximum times.  Unlike individual Lucent Beams, Eclipse does not stun.  Eclipse turns day into night for 10 seconds.\n\nUpgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.",
