        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_night_stalker_hunter_in_the_night_Description": "Night Stalker ist in der Nacht in seinem Element, während der er mit großer Gewandtheit angreift und sich bewegt.",
        "[english]DOTA_Tooltip_ability_night_stalker_hunter_in_the_night_Description": "Night Stalker is in his element at night, attacking and moving with great swiftness.",
        "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_night_stalker_hunter_in_the_night_bonus_movement_speed_pct_night": "%BEWEGUNGSTEMPO:",
